    public class EditProduct
extends AddProduct
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    EditProduct extends AddProduct. It gets the selected Row in the DataTable. The Data from the selected Row is loaded in the TextFields to make Changes easy. It implements two more TextFields to add or remove a certain amount.
